text: Daniel Gaysinsky (born September 3, 1994) is a Canadian karateka. In 2019 he won the silver medal in the men's kumite +84 kg event at the 2019 Pan American Games held in Lima, Peru. == References == == External links == * Category:Living people Category:1994 births Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Canadian male karateka Category:Pan American Games medalists in karate Category:Pan American Games silver medalists for Canada Category:Karateka at the 2019 Pan American Games
